name: Experiment Or Die #11
description: I've had a chance to travel a fair amount, mostly in the US, and I tend to take photos of landmarks, signs and really random things like power lines and sewer grates. I was never really sure what these photos were going to be for but I had an inherent desire to capture images and moments so one day I might utilize them in some way. This project in many ways is an abstract regurgitation of those moments and perhaps seeing things in a new may might bring new meaning to them. IG: Nikejerk
